#### Решение #1 (Python)
```python
def f(x, A):
    return (130 <= x <= 171) <= (((150 <= x <= 185) and (x not in A)) <= (not (130 <= x <= 171)))


A = []
for i in range(1, 10000):
    i = i / 10
    if not f(i, A):
        A.append(i)

print(A)
```
